description:
Danny and Whitney meet for an EMERGENCY bonus episode of Everything Iconic to discuss this week's #RHONY episode, a new holiday classic that will be watched on many Christmases to come alongside It's A Wonderful Life and Miracle on 34th Street.

*For bonus episodes, join the Patreon at www.Patreon.com/EverythingIconic Web: www.EverythingIconic.com Twitter: www.Twitter.com/DannyPellegrino Instagram: www.Instagram.com/DannyPellegrino
